  dialogueLines:
  - Speaker: Barista
    Text: The obvious trail is usually bait.
  - Speaker: Rina
    Text: Look instead for the places people maintain with devotion and explain with
      discomfort.
  choices:
  - choiceText: I understand. I will look closer.
    nextDialogue: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 4509f7dd12b93d64db04af99d80802c7, type: 2}
